{
  "name": "validate-naming",
  "description": "Validates naming conventions for MASE plugin",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "trigger": "onFileSave",
  "filePattern": "**/*.{php,js,css}",
  "excludePattern": "**/vendor/**,**/node_modules/**,**/tests/**",
  "enabled": true,
  "prompt": "You are validating naming conventions for MASE v1.2.0.\n\n**FILE:** {{filePath}}\n**FILE TYPE:** {{fileExtension}}\n\n**NAMING CONVENTIONS:**\n\n**PHP:**\n- Classes: `MASE_Palette_Manager` (MASE_ prefix + PascalCase)\n- Methods: `get_palette_colors()` (snake_case)\n- Variables: `$palette_id` (snake_case)\n- Constants: `MAX_PALETTE_COUNT` (SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE)\n- Files: `class-mase-palette-manager.php` (kebab-case)\n\n**JavaScript:**\n- Objects: `MASEAdmin` (PascalCase)\n- Variables: `paletteManager` (camelCase)\n- Functions: `getPaletteColors()` (camelCase)\n- Constants: `MAX_PALETTE_COUNT` (SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE)\n- Files: `mase-admin.js` (kebab-case)\n\n**CSS:**\n- Classes: `.mase-palette-card` (kebab-case with mase- prefix)\n- IDs: `#mase-settings-panel` (kebab-case with mase- prefix)\n- Variables: `--mase-primary-color` (kebab-case with --mase- prefix)\n- Files: `mase-palettes.css` (kebab-case)\n\n**YOUR TASK:**\n1. Scan file for naming convention violations\n2. Check classes, methods, variables, constants\n3. Verify file naming\n4. Provide specific fixes\n\n**OUTPUT FORMAT:**\n```\n✅ PASS / ❌ FAIL: Naming Convention Validation\n\nFile: {{fileName}}\nType: {{fileType}}\n\n[VIOLATIONS FOUND]\n\n1. Line XX: Class name violation\n   Current: PaletteManager\n   Expected: MASE_Palette_Manager\n   Rule: PHP classes must have MASE_ prefix and use PascalCase\n\n2. Line YY: Method name violation\n   Current: getPalette()\n   Expected: get_palette()\n   Rule: PHP methods must use snake_case\n\n3. Line ZZ: Variable name violation\n   Current: $paletteID\n   Expected: $palette_id\n   Rule: PHP variables must use snake_case\n\n[SUMMARY]\nTotal violations: {{count}}\n- Classes: {{class_count}}\n- Methods: {{method_count}}\n- Variables: {{var_count}}\n- Constants: {{const_count}}\n\n[REQUIRED FIXES]\n[List all fixes needed]\n\n[FILE NAMING]\n✅/❌ File name follows convention: {{status}}\n```\n\nBe specific with line numbers and provide exact corrections."
}
